Find the limit:
 \(\displaystyle \lim_{x \rightarrow 0^{+}} x^{$a} \ln x = \)
\{ ans_rule(35) \}
$BR
${BITALIC}(Enter ${BBOLD}undefined$EBOLD if the limit does not exist.)$EITALIC

